                "to": "pgraff@reliantenergy.com",
                "subject": "Re: Master Agreement",
                "body_text": "[Historical email excerpt]\nI did receive your e-mails and apologize for my late response.  Yes, I will \nbe the negotiating person for the agreement with the exception of credit \nterms and issues, but will also be involved in the background with credit.  \n\nI hope to  e-mail you my comments by the end of next week.\n\nRegards,\nDebra Perlingiere\nEnron North America Corp.\n1400 Smith Street, EB 3885\nHouston, Texas 77002\ndperlin@enron.com\nPhone 713-853-7658\nFax  713-646-3490\n\n[Excerpt limited by source data. Original body may be longer.]\n\nEvent type: message_reply",
